From: "TempleTerry[x64]" <123938029+PhilipPanda@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sat, 21 Mar 2026 05:46:15 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] 9056: Fix typo: "occured" -> "occurred" across codebase

Corrects 46 instances of the misspelling "occured" (should be "occurred")
in 35 Java source files, scripts, and documentation files.
